Detailed Description

cvmx_pki_cl::_pcam::_match#

This register configures the match side of the PCAM. PKI hardware is opaque as to the use of the 32 bits of CAM data.

For each legal j and k, PKI_CL(i)_PCAM(j)_MATCH(k) must be configured identically for i=0..1.
